   CITIBANK-PROBE (Washington) _ Two congressional investigations,
launched from different starting points, are examining Citibank and
the confidential world of private banking, a growing and highly
lucrative service. The investigations, led by lawmakers who rarely
find common cause, are examining how Citibank _ and a handful of
