   MEMPHIS-MAYOR (Memphis, Tenn.) _ Seventeen candidates will
appear on the ballot for the winner-take-all Memphis mayoral
election, but it will really be a showdown _ the first real one _
between two of the strongest black political factions in this
mostly black city. By Emily Yellin.
