   ROSENFELD-SHORTTAKES _ A couple of days ago I heard on the radio
that one of our great universities was offering a certificate for a
course on building web sites. In other words, people can now be
properly certified for doing what they already are doing.
(Rosenfeld, Cox News Service) MOVED MONDAY.
</P>
<P>
   SCHUETT-COLUMN _ GIBSONBURG, Ohio _ Kristofor is my one and only
kid, so I've never married anybody off before. I don't know about
wedding stuff. When friends ask if I'm ready for the big day, I ask
them, what's to get ready? His father is handling the rehearsal
supper from Georgia, and if I have a dress and directions to
DuBois, Penn., the bride-to-be's hometown, what else do I need? I'm
just the mother of the groom and I'm quite familiar with my job
specifications: Wear beige and keep my mouth shut. (Schuett, Cox
News Service) MOVED.
</P>
