<DOCNO> NYT19990727.0079 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-27 13:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5334 &Cx1f; ttf-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TRAIN-FOR-TWO-NYTSF &LR;      07-27 1122
