set, 34-year-old Sharon Tiso could contain herself no longer. After
all, a 500-pound mountain of a professional wrestler known as The
Big Show had just lifted World Wrestling Federation owner Vince
McMahon off the ground like a lumpy sack of potatoes. And as Tiso
and millions of other viewers knew well, McMahon is the bitter
enemy of Stone Cold Steve Austin, wrestling's nihilist Texas
glamour guy, because he doesn't much care for Austin's attitude. So
what's a mother to do, especially one who's a Stone Cold Steve
Austin adulator?
