Dimension desktop or Inspiron notebook. Prices for Dell's Dimension
PCs with Dellnet service begin at $959 or $29 a month. Dellnet also
includes 20MBs of online backup service to protect customers
against data loss and remote access to their information from other
computers. (Mahoney, Austin American-Statesman).
