question entering a season _ when will the Vols win the big one?
Tennessee finally won the big one last season, defeating Florida
State to win the national championship, and the team has several
key players returning in hopes of winning another title. (Barnhart,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 18.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-SEC-GEORGIA _ BIRMINGHAM _ Last season, Quincy Carter was a
virtual unknown, having spent three seasons away from football as a
professional baseball player. Now the Georgia sophomore quaterback
is being mentioned as a Heisman Trophy candidate. Carter, last
season's SEC freshman of the year, is now regarded as one of the
top quarterbacks in the nation and will make his first appearance
at the SEC media days. (Towers, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 16.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-SEC-SALARIES _ Despite finishing third in the SEC East last
season, the Georgia Bulldogs have the second highest total in the
entire conference in football coaches' salary. The hiring of
defensive coordinator Kevin Ramsey from Tennessee and the pay
raises to Rodney Garner and Brad Lambert to keep them from
accepting other offers pushed Georgia to second in the SEC behind
national champion Tennessee. A look at coaches' salaries throughout
the SEC. (Towers, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
