<HEADLINE>
HOUSE BACKS CLINTON'S DECISION TO RENEW NORMAL TRADE WITH CHINA 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: Filed in ``w'' and ``f'' categories.)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
