   MIDEAST-SUMMIT _ EREZ CROSSING POINT, Israel _ With tensions
rising and pressure building for progress in the Mideast peace
process, new Israeli Prime Minister Ehud Barak meets Palestinian
Authority President Yasser Arafat Tuesday night to discuss the next
step. (Kaplow, Cox News Service). 20.
</P>
<P>
   EDs: To move after meeting ends; about 7 p.m. EDT.
