<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    U.S., RUSSIA SET NEW TALKS ON REDUCING NUCLEAR ARMS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (i) international categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
