<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-27 21:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6045 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OIL-ROYALTIES28-COX     07-27 0387
