<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-27 21:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6048 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OBIT-WOLF-NYT &LR;      07-27 0470
