   (NYT8) NEW YORK -- July 27, 1999 -- CHEF-WANNABES-2, 07-27 --
Dr. Bert Goldfinger takes a blowtorch to creme brulee at Le Cirque
2000, as Jacques Torres gives advice. Goldfinger participates a new
program places chef wannabes in the world's most celestial
kitchens, for a price. (Don Hogan Charles/New York Times Photo)
